{
  "key": 21538,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_BurmyInterestingExample",
      "en_US": [
        "Hmmm... The Pokémon BURMY is an\n",
        "interesting example...\r",
        "It hints at how the environment can\n",
        "shape people’s personalities."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_DoYouHaveAllBurmy",
      "en_US": [
        "You know that Pokémon BURMY, and how\n",
        "it comes in different forms?\r",
        "Do you have all the forms of that\n",
        "BURMY?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_NotASingleBurmy",
      "en_US": [
        "Aww, you don’t even have a single\n",
        "BURMY?\r",
        "What, you don’t like them?\n",
        "They’re all mooshy and cute!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_CoolIfDifferentBurmy",
      "en_US": [
        "Hmm...\r",
        "It’d be cool if you had all the\n",
        "different-looking BURMY."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_ThatsAllBurmy",
      "en_US": [
        "Cool! That’s all the different kinds\n",
        "of BURMY! I feel giddy!\r",
        "Since I feel so giddy, take this!\n",
        "Go ahead, take it!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_BagIsCrammedFull",
      "en_US": [
        "Whoops, your Bag is crammed full!\n",
        "I’ll give this to you later."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SunyshoreCityHouse1_Text_YoureGood",
      "en_US": [
        "You’re good!\n",
        "You’d make an awesome Bug Maniac!"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
